rule_des_lottery.EN: 1. The base number of coins changes after each draw.\n\n2.The lottery is limited up to 3 times per day.
rule_des_lottery.CN: 1.每次进行金币抽奖后金币基数都会发生改变。\n\n2.金币抽奖每日上限3次。

rule_des_vip.EN:
1. The VIP Card is valid for 30 days from the day of purchase.

2.The VIP Card can only be purchased once within 30 days.

3.The daily rewards of the VIP Card will be refreshed every day after 0:00.
rule_des_vip.CN:
1.黄金月卡有效期为购买当日起算30天。

2.黄金月卡30天内只能购买一次。

3.黄金月卡的每日奖励将在每日0点后刷新。

rule_des_piggybank.EN:
1. You can deposit coins into the piggy bank if you pass level successfully.

2.After collecting {0} gold coins, you can buy a piggy bank at a discounted price.

3.After the piggy bank is full, no coins can be collected.
rule_des_piggybank.CN:
1.成功过关可以向猪猪储蓄罐存入金币。

2.收集满 {0} 金币后您可用实惠的价格购买猪猪储蓄罐。

3.猪猪储蓄罐存满后无法在再收集额外的金币。

rule_des_luckywheel.EN:
1. There is a 30-minute cooling time after each spin.

2.The Lucky Wheel has a daily limit of 5 times.

3.Monthly Golden Ticket holders can obtain extra lucky chests.

4. Rewards are refreshed every day at 0:00.
rule_des_luckywheel.CN:
1.转动幸运大转盘后需等30分钟才能再次转动。

2.幸运大转盘每日上限5次。

3.黄金月卡可以额外获取幸运宝箱。

4.幸运大转盘宝箱奖励每日0点后刷新。

rule_des_bignner.EN:
1. You can get coin and booster rewards immediately by purchasing Beginner Bundle. 

2. Additional daily rewards can be collected in three consecutive days, starting from the second day after purchase. 

3. The reward of the day will be invalid if it's not collected within each day.
rule_des_bignner.CN:
1.购买新手礼包即可立即获得大量金币和道具奖励。

2.从礼包购买后的第二天开始，连续三天，每天可获得额外奖励。

3.若领取时间内未领取当天奖励，则该奖励失效，无法领取。

guide_dialog_105.EN: Welcome to Ella's wondrous holiday, tap on the indicated area to drop the animal. The same kind will be merged.
guide_dialog_105.CN: 欢迎来到小动物乐合合，点击指示区域放下小动物，相同的动物就会合成哦！

guide_dialog_109.EN: Look, the level goal is in the top right corner. We can pass the level if we complete all the goals.
guide_dialog_109.CN: 看，右上方是关卡目标。我们已经完成了一个，全部完成就过关了。

guide_dialog_301.EN: Here are some old wooden boxes! They were used on the farm long ago. Let's take them down together.
guide_dialog_301.CN: 这有些以前农场里装东西的废旧木箱，我们一起把它们拆除掉。

guide_dialog_302.EN: We can tear down the wooden boxes by merging next to them.
guide_dialog_302.CN: 在木箱旁合成可以把它拆除掉。

guide_dialog_501.EN: New item unlocked! Hammer can clean animals or objects. Try it!
guide_dialog_501.CN: 木锤子已解锁，它可以消除一个动物或物品，试试看。

guide_dialog_601.EN: It's time to make omelets, but we don't have enough eggs. Let's get some more.
guide_dialog_601.CN: 我想做一些蛋饼，但是屋里的鸡蛋用完了，我们得再去拿一些鸡蛋。

guide_dialog_602.EN: When the eggs fall to the bottom border, we can take them away.
guide_dialog_602.CN: 让鸡蛋掉到底部的边框，我们就可以拿走它们了。

guide_dialog_1001.EN: Grandpa wanna make honey cakes, but the honey pot is not in the kitchen. Go and fetch him some honey!
guide_dialog_1001.CN: 爷爷想做蜂蜜蛋糕给我们吃，可是蜂蜜罐不在厨房。帮他去拿几罐蜂蜜回来吧！

guide_dialog_1002.EN: Merge animals next to the honey pot can get them!
guide_dialog_1002.CN: 在蜂蜜罐旁合成可以获取蜂蜜罐。

guide_dialog_1401.EN: Oops, the grinder and the plank fell into the water! Ahhh... Let's figure it out.
guide_dialog_1401.CN: 我的碎木机和木板掉进了水里！啊…一起想想办法吧。

guide_dialog_1402.EN: See those empty bottles? Merge beside them to lower the water level.
guide_dialog_1402.CN: 看到那些空瓶子了吗？在它们旁边合成，就可以让水位降下来。

guide_dialog_1801.EN: Would you like some strawberry pie? I really love it! We need to pick some strawberries!
guide_dialog_1801.CN: 想不想尝尝祖父的草莓派？我们需要采一些草莓！

guide_dialog_1802.EN: Collect strawberries by merging next to the strawberry jelly. You can collect a lot at once!
guide_dialog_1802.CN: 在草莓果冻旁合成可以采集草莓，一次可以采集很多哦！

guide_dialog_1901.EN: Guess what accessories I bought for the animals? They're so cute, let me show you!
guide_dialog_1901.CN: 你猜猜我给小动物们新买了些什么小装饰？简直太可爱了，我带你去看看！

guide_dialog_1902.EN: Isn't it fun? Merge them to get the sunglasses.
guide_dialog_1902.CN: 是不是很好玩？合成它们，可以把小墨镜拿回来。

guide_dialog_2001.EN: Grandpa asked us to carry some grinders for making wood supplies. Let's speed up the processing of the plank.
guide_dialog_2001.CN: 祖父让我们帮他搬一些碎木机，他需要做一些木质用品。我们先加速把眼下的木板处理完。

guide_dialog_2002.EN: Merging next to the grinder and the plank can start the grinder to break the plank.
guide_dialog_2002.CN: 在碎木机和木板旁合成，可以让碎木机工作，把木板碎掉。

guide_dialog_2601.EN: The grass has been eaten up, let's seed a new lawn, haha!
guide_dialog_2601.CN: 有些草地被动物吃光了，我们试试搞点绿化工作，哈哈！

guide_dialog_2602.EN: The drops merge can spread out the turf!
guide_dialog_2602.CN: 合成可以让草皮逐渐铺开来！

guide_dialog_2801.EN: Wow, what's that? A...Cute little monster?
guide_dialog_2801.CN: 天哪，那是什么？一只...可爱的小怪兽？

guide_dialog_2802.EN: It wants us to create some drops generation for him.
guide_dialog_2802.CN: 它好像希望我们帮它合成一些动物，尽量满足它的愿望吧。

guide_dialog_2901.EN: What a lovely day! Come on, let's pull up the curtains.
guide_dialog_2901.CN: 这会儿阳光这么好，走，我们把窗帘都拉起来。

guide_dialog_2902.EN: The drops effect can roll up the curtains.
guide_dialog_2902.CN: 合成可以让窗帘逐步收起。

guide_dialog_2201.EN: The coin could buy the power booster, so let's find out where we can get more coins.
guide_dialog_2201.CN: 金币可以购买各种常用道具，我们去找找哪里能搞到更多金币。

guide_dialog_2204.EN: Wow, this looks like a good way to get coins! Take a chance!
guide_dialog_2204.CN: 哇哦，这个看起来能弄到不少金币，碰碰运气！

guide_dialog_2206.EN: You are so lucky! Check out more details here.
guide_dialog_2206.CN: 你果然是幸运体质！这里可以看到更多详细游戏规则。

guide_dialog_2301.EN: Happy people are always lucky. Let me show you something nice!
guide_dialog_2301.CN: 快乐的人的运气一般都很好，所以我想你帮我去看一个好东西！

guide_dialog_2304.CN: 转一下，看看你的幸运女神还在不在身边。

guide_dialog_2306.EN: Winning again! Try it every 30 minutes. Good luck!
guide_dialog_2306.CN: 幸运体质！又中奖啦！每隔30分钟都可以来试一次，祝你好运哦！

guide_dialog_2605.EN: Tap here to get tips. Remember this order that will help you with coming level. (Tap anywhere to close the tips)
guide_dialog_2605.CN: 在这里我们可以查看小动物们的合成顺序哦，点击任意位置即可关闭气泡框。

guide_ball1.EN: 4 X COMBO generates the Red Energy Booster.

guide_ball2.EN: The Red Energy Booster can level up the touched animal.
guide_ball2.CN: 红色能量瓶可以让碰到的动物变高一级。

guide_ball3.EN: 5 X COMBO generates the Blue Energy Booster.

guide_ball4.EN: The Blue Energy Booster can upgrade the animal at the bottom directly.
guide_ball4.CN: 蓝色能量瓶可以直接升级最下方的动物，有时候比红色能量瓶更好用。

guide_ball5.EN: 6 X COMBO generates the Rainbow Energy Booster.

guide_ball6.EN: Rainbow Energy Booster can upgrade all animals of the selected one kind.
guide_ball6.CN: 彩色能量瓶可以让所有同类动物都一起升级，是最珍贵的能量瓶。

guide_dialog_4001.EN: Stones and bombs. . . Any connection between them?
guide_dialog_4001.CN: 看到这些石头和炸弹没有，它们之间……好像有什么联系？

guide_dialog_4002.EN: You can destroy a random stone by merging next to the bomb! Try it!
guide_dialog_4002.CN: 在炸弹旁边合成，就可以随机炸毁一块石头哦，试试看。

guide_dialog_4101.EN: Lucky you! You met the legendary totem!
guide_dialog_4101.CN: 运气真好，竟然碰见了传说中的图腾！

guide_dialog_4102.EN: Merge beside the totem to split it. It can be split 2 times. Let's collect the smallest totem!
guide_dialog_4102.CN: 在图腾周围合成就可以分裂图腾，图腾一共可以分裂2次，让我们把最小的图腾收集起来吧。

guide_dialog_4201.EN: Grandpa asked us to decorate our home. Collect these lights to make our home more beautiful!
guide_dialog_4201.CN: 爷爷让我们为家里做些装饰，收集这些灯，来漂亮地装扮家吧。

guide_dialog_4202.EN: Merge beside the light to change its color. We can collect the lights when all of them become one color.
guide_dialog_4202.CN: 在灯旁边合成就能使它变色，当所有灯变为一个颜色的时候就能收集它们啦。

guide_dialog_4301.EN: Glass pieces are blocking the animals! Try to break the glass!
guide_dialog_4301.CN: 这些玻璃挡住了小动物们的脸，让我们来把它敲碎吧。

guide_dialog_4302.EN: The glass will shatter if you merge in the glass area.
guide_dialog_4302.CN: 在玻璃范围内合成玻璃就会破碎哦。

guide_dialog_4401.EN: These canned tomatoes look delicious. We can bring some back for Grandpa!
guide_dialog_4401.CN: 这些西红柿罐头看起来很好吃，我们给爷爷带一些回去。

guide_dialog_4402.EN: Merge around them to collect the tomatoes inside. There are 3 tomatoes in each can.
guide_dialog_4402.CN: 在它们周围发生合成就能收集里面的西红柿，每个罐头里都有3个西红柿哦。

guide_dialog_4501.EN: Wow! Puzzle pieces! It must be fun!
guide_dialog_4501.CN: 这里竟然有拼图，看起来很好玩？

guide_dialog_4502.EN: See the puzzle packs? Merge beside them to put the pieces together. Have fun!
guide_dialog_4502.CN: 看到那些拼图包没，在它们旁边合成就能把拼图拼起来，一起来玩吧！

item_des_206.EN: BOMB damages and pushes obstacles around it
item_des_206.CN: 彩弹合成后会爆炸，可以破坏或崩飞旁边的东西。

item_des_208.EN: The Rocket will find an obstacle to destroy
item_des_208.CN: 火箭合成后会引燃，可以精准寻找并破坏一个目标。

item_des_207.EN: TNT can make a cross-shaped explosion to blow up and destroy things around.
item_des_207.CN: 炸药合成后会爆炸，可以破坏横竖方向的东西。

item_des_308.EN: Frisbee can remove one layer of any obstacle on the selected row without using a move.
item_des_308.CN: 飞盘会命中指定横向范围内的所有物品

outnotice_des3.CN: 快来和他们一起冒险吧！\uD83C\uDF81

outnotice_des4.EN: Come and challenge the new levels!\uD83D\uDE3B

guide1_booster1.EN: BOMB damages and pushes obstacles around it.
guide1_booster1.CN: 小彩弹合成后会爆炸，可以破坏或崩飞旁边的东西。

guide1_booster11.EN: Drop animals to touch the same color BOMB can explode the surroundings.
guide1_booster11.CN: 小彩弹可以被相同颜色的动物引爆

guide1_booster2.EN: Rocket will find an obstacle to destroy.
guide1_booster2.CN: 小火箭合成后会引燃，可以精准寻找并破坏一个目标。

guide1_booster3.EN: TNT can make a cross-shaped explosion to blow up and destroy things around.
guide1_booster3.CN: 小炸药合成后会爆炸，可以破坏横竖方向的东西。

guide_dialog_5701.EN: Touch to unlock the Energy ball.
guide_dialog_5701.CN: 能量球已解锁，每次合成动物都会增加能量哦，试试看。

guide1_booster5.EN: Energy balls to fill it up and get extra help!
guide1_booster5.CN: 能量球加满后会直接生成道具，使我们的游戏更轻松！

guide_dialog_701.EN: You've unlocked the Magic Hat, and it can upgrade any animal directly.
guide_dialog_701.CN: 魔术帽已解锁，它可以让任意一只动物直接升级。

guide_dialog_1601.EN: You've unlocked the Frisbee and Dart. Try the Frisbee, it can destroy the obstacles in a horizontal line.
guide_dialog_1601.CN: 飞盘和飞镖已解锁，先来试试飞盘，它可以破坏横向范围的所有物品。

guide_dialog_1605.EN: Then try the Dart, it can destroy all items in a vertical line.
guide_dialog_1605.CN: 再试试飞镖，它可以破坏竖向范围的所有物品。

guide1_booster9.EN: Crystal Ball's trial is over, you can continue to enjoy it by activating the VIP Card!
guide1_booster9.CN: 预知试用时间已结束，激活黄金月卡可以继续免费享受哦！

guide_dialog_401.EN: Boosters have been unlocked, and they can help you!
guide_dialog_401.CN: 战前道具已经解锁啦，它们可以助你一臂之力！

guide_dialog_5101.EN: Combo balls can produce unexpected effects with props!
guide_dialog_5101.CN: COMBO球可以和道具产生意想不到的效果哦！

guide_dialog_801.EN: You have got the Crystal Ball, now you can know exactly what's next drop.
guide_dialog_801.CN: 你获得了限时预知效果，现在你可以预知到下一个掉落物是什么啦！

guide_dialog_106.EN: There are wooden boxes. We can tear down the wooden boxes by merging animals next to them.
guide_dialog_106.CN: 这里有一些木箱，我们可以在旁边合成打碎它们。

guide_dialog_1137.EN: The level goal is in the upper right corner.Now try to make it through by eliminating the remaining wooden boxes.
guide_dialog_1137.CN: 看，关卡目标在右上角。现在来尝试通过合成小动消除剩余木箱来通过关卡吧。

guide_dialog_001.EN: Hi, I'm Ella! I live on a farm with my grandpa, Professor Stevenson.
guide_dialog_001.CN: Hi，我是Ella，我和我的外公Stevenson教授一起住在我们的农场里。

guide_dialog_002.EN: Grandpa is a biologist, so we have many animal friends.
guide_dialog_002.CN: 我外公是个生物学家，我们有很多动物伙伴。

guide_dialog_003.EN: Hi, I am Stevenson. What's your name?
guide_dialog_003.CN: 你好，我是Stevenson。你叫什么名字？

guide_dialog_004.EN: Welcome, {username}. We've prepared an adventure trip this summer vacation. Let's go!
guide_dialog_004.CN: 欢迎你，{username}。今年暑假我们准备了一次冒险旅行。

guide_dialog_0040.EN: Of course, we'll bring our animal friends. Let's meet them first!
guide_dialog_0040.CN: 当然，必须带上我们的动物伙伴们，让我们先来认识一下它们！

guide_dialog_005.EN: You see, these are my animal friends! We just received 3 stars with their help!
guide_dialog_005.CN: 是的，这就是我的动物伙伴，它们刚才帮我获得了3颗星星。

guide_dialog_006.EN: Let's see what the stars do.
guide_dialog_006.CN: 让我们看看星星有什么作用吧。

guide_dialog_007.EN: Stars can light up a part of the postcard!

guide_dialog_008.EN: Wow! It's me! We need more stars to light up other parts of the postcard.
guide_dialog_008.CN: 哇，这是我诶！我还需要更多星星！

guide_dialog_011.EN: Isn't my cat cute? She's listening to my song.
guide_dialog_011.CN: 我的猫咪可爱吗？它在听我的音乐！

guide_dialog_013.EN: My sheep is here, there must be other friends.
guide_dialog_013.CN: 我的羊也在，一定还有其他伙伴。

guide_dialog_014.EN: Cool! We can light up a new part of the postcard now!
guide_dialog_014.CN: 哇！我们可以点亮新的部分了！

guide_dialog_015.EN: Who says cows don't listen to music? By the way, why is the background not colored?
guide_dialog_015.CN: 谁说牛不听音乐的？对了，为什么背景不是彩色的？

guide_dialog_016.EN: This time we've got enough stars, I guess.

guide_dialog_017.EN: A postcard with a gift! Awesome! Many postcards are waiting for us to find during the vacation!
guide_dialog_017.CN: 明信片还附带礼物，太棒啦！还有好多明信片等着我们在旅途中发现！

guide_dialog_019.EN: Okay, let's start our trip. I'll collect a great many stars!
guide_dialog_019.CN: 好的，让我们开始旅行吧，我会有很多很多星星的。

guide_dialog_020.EN: Finally out of the farm, so where is our first stop.
guide_dialog_020.CN: 终于走出农场了，那么我们第一次站是哪里呢。

guide_dialog_022.EN: The pyramids are so mysterious, but it's a bit hot.
guide_dialog_022.CN: 金字塔真是太神秘了，只是有点热。

guide_dialog_023.EN: Then let's go to the beach next stop. I'll drop in on my old friend.
guide_dialog_023.CN: 那么我们下一站就去海边吧，我顺便拜访一下我的老朋友。

guide_dialog_024.EN: I love the sea. I wish I could live here forever
guide_dialog_024.CN: 我好喜欢大海，能够永远住在这里就好了。

guide_dialog_025.EN: As long as there's no storm…Do you wanna go somewhere colder?
guide_dialog_025.CN: 只要没有暴风雨。想不想去冷一点的地方？

guide_dialog_10500.EN: Tap on the indicated area to drop the animal. The same kind will be merged.
guide_dialog_10500.CN: 点击指示区域放下小动物，相同的动物就会合成哦！

animalfriend_des.EN: Collect {0} animals to win the rewards! Complete all steps to win the Grand Prize!
animalfriend_des.CN: 收集{0}个动物赢得奖励，完成所有阶段还能获得大奖！

animalfriend_failed_des.EN: You will lose the animal rewards collected this time!
animalfriend_failed_des.CN: 你收集了足够多的动物获得奖励，你将会失去它们！

booster_des.EN: It's time to test your skills! Use boosters to improve rankings and get rewards!
booster_des.CN: 使用道具冲刺排名，排名越高能获得的奖励越丰厚哦！

guide_dialog_7501.EN: Let me give you some help!

guide_dialog_7502.EN: See these gift boxes? Open them to get mysterious items!
guide_dialog_7502.CN: 看到这些礼物盒了吗？打开它们将会获得神秘道具！

guide_dialog_7601.EN: Some things are trapped in the iron cage, try to take them out.
guide_dialog_7601.CN: 有些东西被困在铁笼里了，想办法拿出来。

guide_dialog_7602.EN: Merge beside the iron cage to break it.
guide_dialog_7602.CN: 在铁笼旁边合成可以击破铁笼。

guide_dialog_7701.EN: The animals are frozen, help them out!
guide_dialog_7701.CN: 小动物们被冻住了，想办法帮帮它们！

guide_dialog_7702.EN: Merge beside frozen animals to unfreeze them.
guide_dialog_7702.CN: 在冻住的动物旁边合成可以解除冰冻。

guide_dialog_7801.EN: I need some ice cubes for shaved ice. But the ice machine sometimes goes wrong and freezes something else.
guide_dialog_7801.CN: 我想搞点冰块制作刨冰。但制冰机有时候会失灵，冻住一些东西。

guide_dialog_7802.EN: Merge beside the ice machine to collect the ice cubes inside.
guide_dialog_7802.CN: 在制冰机旁边合成可以收集里面的冰块。

guide_dialog_7901.EN: Why not add more drops using your coins? Try it free this time!
guide_dialog_7901.CN: 花费金币可以增加步数，这次免费帮你加步数吧！

gift_2.EN: Beat levels on your first try to earn grandpa's boosters!
gift_2.CN: 一次通关获得神秘过关奖励！

guide_dialog_4601.EN: Grandpa brought some seeds. Let's plant beautiful flowers!
guide_dialog_4601.CN: 祖父带来了一些花朵种子，让我们来种植漂亮的花朵吧！

guide_dialog_4602.EN: Merge beside the flowerpots will help the flowers grow. Grow all connected flowers to take away these pots!
guide_dialog_4602.CN: 在花盆旁合成开始种植，当连在一起的花盆上的花全部盛开时这些花盆就会消失！

ellaguitar_rule.EN: Beat one level and earn a note to participate in the competetion!
ellaguitar_rule.CN: 通过一个关卡，获得音符，即可参加比赛。

ellaguitar_rule1.EN: Triple notes for beating a level on your first try!
ellaguitar_rule1.CN: 第一次尝试就通过关卡，可以获得3倍音符奖励结算。

ellaguitar_rule2.EN: Double notes for beating a level on your second tries!
ellaguitar_rule2.CN: 第二次尝试通过关卡，可以获得2倍音符奖励结算。

ellaguitar_rule3.EN: Regular notes for beating a level on your third or more tries!
ellaguitar_rule3.CN: 第三次及以上尝试通过关卡，获得1倍音符奖励结算。

ellaguitar_rule_ingame.EN: Merge animals to get notes. Start your play now!
ellaguitar_rule_ingame.CN: 小动物合成即可获得音符，保持连胜！

ellaguitar_victory1.EN: Congratulations! You have reached to a higher league! The rewards will be more generous next round!
ellaguitar_victory1.CN: 祝贺你晋级更高联盟，接下来的比赛中，奖励会更加丰厚！

ellaguitar_victory2.EN: Congratulations! Keep up with the race and get better rewards!
ellaguitar_victory2.CN: 恭喜，继续参加比赛保持名次，获得更好的奖励！

ellaguitar_lose.EN: It's okay! cheer up next time!
ellaguitar_lose.CN: 别灰心，继续参加下次比赛，提升名次。

ellaguitar_rule4.EN: Try reaching the higher league to get richer prizes. Players fall behind will be demoted to the lower league.
ellaguitar_rule4.CN: 获得更多音符，在排行榜上名列前茅，即可升入更高联盟，获得更丰厚的奖品。排名靠后的玩家则会降低至更低的联盟。

ellaguitar_leagueup.EN: Players above will raise to higher league
ellaguitar_leagueup.CN: 以上玩家升入更高联盟。

ellaguitar_leaguedown.EN: Players below will fall to lower league
ellaguitar_leaguedown.CN: 以下玩家降低至更低联盟。

kite_noreward.CN: 以下玩家无法获得奖励

kite_noteam.EN: Join a team of more than 10 players to participate in Above the Clouds!
kite_noteam.CN: 加入10人以上队伍，参与风筝大赛！

kite_noteammember.EN: Your team is less than 10 players! Gather 10 players to start the event!
kite_noteammember.CN: 你的队伍不足10人，集齐10名队员就能开启风筝大赛！

kite_start.EN: Above the Clouds has begun! Beat a level to help your team fly a kite!
kite_start.CN: 风筝大赛开始了！通关一关即可开启风筝大赛！

kite_nojoin.EN: You cannot get rewards of this round of Above the Clouds.
kite_nojoin.CN: 很遗憾，你将无法获得本次风筝大赛活动奖励。

kite_leave_team.EN: You won't be able to compete in Above the Clouds.
kite_leave_team.CN: 现在离开，你将失去参加风筝大赛的资格。

teamrace_noteam.EN: Join a team of more than 10 players to participate in Team Race!
teamrace_noteam.CN: 加入10人以上队伍，参与队伍大冒险！

teamrace_noteammember.EN: Your team is less than 10 players! Gather 10 players to start the event!
teamrace_noteammember.CN: 你的队伍不足10人，集齐10名队员就能开启队伍大冒险！

teamrace_start.EN: Team Race has begun! Beat a level to join Team Race!
teamrace_start.CN: 队伍大冒险开始了！通关一关即可开启队伍大冒险！

teamrace_nojoin.EN: You cannot get rewards of this round of Team Race.
teamrace_nojoin.CN: 很遗憾，你将无法获得本次队伍大冒险活动奖励。

teamrace_leave_team.EN: You won't be able to compete  in Team Race.
teamrace_leave_team.CN: 现在离开，你将失去参加队伍大冒险的资格。

diamondrush_start.EN: Diamond Rush has begun! Beat a level to join Diamond Rush!
diamondrush_start.CN: 终极冒险开始了！通关一关即可闯入终极冒险排行榜！

diamondrush_rule.EN: Beat a level to earn a diamond! The more diamonds, the higher your ranking!
diamondrush_rule.CN: 通过一关即可收集一颗钻石！钻石越多，你的排名就越高！

diamondrush_update.EN: This round of Diamond Rush is over! Please update the game to continue playing the new levels and get your reward!
diamondrush_update.CN: 本轮终极冒险已经结束！请更新游戏版本以体验全新的关卡并领取你的奖励！

loading_update.EN: Please update the game and continue playing the new levels!
loading_update.CN: 请更新游戏版本以体验全新的关卡！
